trans-unit.source: Contains all the localizable resources in a BAML record.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller alla lokaliserbara resurser i en BAML-post.

trans-unit.source: The dictionary contains a mapping from resource keys (specified as <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Localizer.BamlLocalizableResourceKey> objects) to resource values (specified as <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Localizer.BamlLocalizableResource> objects).
trans-unit.target: Ordlistan innehåller mappning från resurs-nycklar (angivna som <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Localizer.BamlLocalizableResourceKey>objekt) till resurs-värden (anges som <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Localizer.BamlLocalizableResource>objekt).</xref:System.Windows.Markup.Localizer.BamlLocalizableResource> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.Localizer.BamlLocalizableResourceKey>
